когда<span style='letter-spacing:3.0pt'> собирались <span style='color:#C00000'>у Рузского</span></span><IDXSKIP>!</IDXSKIP></b>”</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
14.2pt'><span style='font-size:13.0pt;'>[<b><span style='color:#C00000'>+</span></b>Генерал Болдырев.]</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:14.2pt'><span
